\c 75
\s UNkulunkulu ungumahluleli
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Alithashethi. Isihlabelelo sikaAsafi, ihubo
\p
\v 1 Siyakubonga, Nkulunkulu, siyabonga, ukuthi ibizo lakho liseduze, iyalandisa imisebenzi yakho emangalisayo\x + Dute. 4.7.\x*.
\v 2 Lapho ngisemukela isikhathi esimisiweyo\x + Hlab. 46.10.\x* ngizakwahlulela ngokuqonda\x + Hlab. 17.2.\x*.
\v 3 Umhlaba labo bonke abakhileyo kuwo kuncibilikile\x + Isa. 24.19.\x*; mina ngiqinisa insika zawo. \w Sela\w**\x + 1 Sam. 2.8. Hlab. 11.3. 82.5.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Ngathi kwabayiziwula: Lingabi yiziwula\x + Hlab. 5.5.\x*. Lakwababi: Lingaphakamisi uphondo\x + 75.10. Zek. 1.21.\x*.
\v 5 Lingaphakamiseli phezulu uphondo lwenu, li\add nga\add*khulum\add i\add* ngentamo\x + Jobe 15.26. Hlab. 73.6.\x* elukhuni\x + 1 Sam. 2.3.\x*.
\v 6 Ngoba ukuphakanyiswa kakuveli empumalanga kumbe entshonalanga njalo hatshi enkangala.
\v 7 Kodwa uNkulunkulu ungumahluleli\x + Hlab. 50.6. Hlab. 76.8,9. Hlab. 58.11.\x*, uyehlisa omunye, aphakamise omunye\x + 1 Sam. 2.7. Dan. 2.21.\x*.
\v 8 Ngoba esandleni seN\nd kosi\x + Jobe 21.20.\x*\nd* kulenkezo\x + Hlab. 11.6. 73.10.\x*; lewayini liphuphuma, ligcwele inhlanganiso; iyathulula okwalo\x + Zaga 23.30.\x*; kodwa izibhidi zalo, ababi bonke bomhlaba bazazihluza bazinathe\x + Hlab. 73.10.\x*.
\p
\v 9 Kodwa mina ngizatshumayela njalonjalo, ngihlabele indumiso kuNkulunkulu kaJakobe.
\v 10 Njalo zonke impondo zababi ngizaziquma\x + Jer. 48.25. Jobe 16.15.\x*; impondo zabalungileyo zizaphakanyiswa\x + 1 Sam. 2.1.\x*.
